"title": "5292: defence, divine",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5292",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God defends his people, especially the most vulnerable. Because of God's defence, although Christians sometimes face trials and persecutions their eternal security is never threatened.</p>\n<h2>God defends his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:10-Isa41:12\">ISA 41:10–41:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:20\">EXO 23:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:27\">EXO 23:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:9\">1SA 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:16-2Kgs6:17\">2KI 6:16–6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:7\">PSA 34:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:10\">PSA 144:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:20\">ISA 19:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:16\">ISA 51:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:22\">ISA 51:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:16-Isa54:17\">ISA 54:16–54:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:34\">JER 50:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:36\">JER 51:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:8\">ZEC 9:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:18\">MAT 16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:28-John10:29\">JHN 10:28–10:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:16-2Tim4:18\">2TI 4:16–4:18</a></p>\n<h2>God defends especially the most vulnerable of his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:17-Ps10:18\">PSA 10:17–10:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:17-Deut10:18\">DEU 10:17–10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:5\">PSA 68:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:9\">PSA 146:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:10-Prov23:11\">PRO 23:10–23:11</a></p>\n<h2>God defended the city of Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:32-2Kgs19:34\">2KI 19:32–19:34</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:33-Isa37:35\">ISA 37:33–37:35</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:6\">2KI 20:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:6\">ISA 38:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:3\">PSA 48:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:5\">ISA 31:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech2:4-Zech2:5\">ZEC 2:4–2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:8\">ZEC 12:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's defence of his people is pictured in various ways</h2>\n<h3>As a hiding-place</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:7\">PSA 32:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:8\">PSA 17:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:5\">PSA 27:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:20\">PSA 31:20</a></p>\n<h3>As a refuge</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:1\">PSA 57:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:27\">DEU 33:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:1\">PSA 46:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:26\">PRO 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:10\">PRO 18:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:16\">JOL 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:7\">NAM 1:7</a></p>\n<h3>As a shield</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:9-Ps115:11\">PSA 115:9–115:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:1\">GEN 15:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:11\">PSA 84:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:114\">PSA 119:114</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:5\">PRO 30:5</a></p>\n<h3>As a combination of images</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:1-2Sam22:4\">2SA 22:1–22:4</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:2-Ps18:3\">PSA 18:2–18:3</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:3\">PSA 71:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:1-Ps91:4\">PSA 91:1–91:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:1-Ps144:2\">PSA 144:1–144:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:4\">ISA 25:4</a></p>\n<h2>The most reliable defence for God's people is to trust only in him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:1\">ISA 31:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:7-2Chr16:9\">2CH 16:7–16:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:6-Ps20:8\">PSA 20:6–20:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:16-Ps37:19\">PSA 37:16–37:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps125:1-Ps125:2\">PSA 125:1–125:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa17:7-Isa17:8\">ISA 17:7–17:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:16-Dan3:18\">DAN 3:16–3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:3\">HOS 14:3</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of prayers for God's defence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:20\">PSA 25:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:14-2Kgs19:19\">2KI 19:14–19:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:14-Isa37:20\">ISA 37:14–37:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:10-2Chr20:12\">2CH 20:10–20:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:17\">2CH 32:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:20\">2CH 32:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:23\">PSA 35:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:22\">PSA 74:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:2\">PSA 86:2</a></p>\n<h2>Because of God's defence the eternal security of believers is never threatened</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:3–1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:28-Matt10:31\">MAT 10:28–10:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:4-Luke12:7\">LUK 12:4–12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:28-John10:29\">JHN 10:28–10:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:15\">JHN 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:31-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:31–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:18\">2TI 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:32-Heb11:39\">HEB 11:32–11:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:8-1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:8–5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:13-Rev7:17\">REV 7:13–7:17</a></p>",
